Files

file  hw_pmhal_data_names.h
 This file contains macros to select module names.
 
file  pmhal_bgap.h
 This file contains the interface declaration for the Temperature HAL.
 
file  pmhal_clocktree.h
 This file contains Acyclic Graph Abstract Data Type, it has the graph node API for tree traversal.
 
file  pmhal_cm.h
 This file contains the prototypes of the APIs present in the device abstraction layer file of PRCM Clock mode. This also contains some related macros.
 
file  pmhal_i2cComm.h
 This file contains the structure and APIs to register I2C handlers with PMHAL.
 
file  pmhal_ina226.h
 This file contains the APIs to program and read the INA226 power measurement ICs.
 
file  pmhal_mm.h
 This file contains the prototypes of the APIs present in the device abstraction layer file of PRCM module mode. This also contains some related macros.
 
file  pmhal_mpu_lprm.h
 This file contains the MPU LPRM interface declarations. The MPU LPRM API supports the following features:
 
file  pmhal_mpu_m3.h
 This file contains the MPU M3 Proxy interface declarations.
 
file  pmhal_pdm.h
 This file contains the prototypes of the APIs present in the device abstraction layer file of Power Domain Manager (PDM).
 
file  pmhal_pmic.h
 This file contains the PMIC API. The PMIC API provides a generic PMIC interface to the users while abstracting the different PMIC HW. A user can bind a specific PMIC HW to this PMIC interface by registering the pmhalPmicOperations_t type with the PMIC module.
 
file  pmhal_pmicComm.h
 This file contains the BUS Read and Write utility functions to communicate with the PMIC.
 
file  pmhal_prcm.h
 
file  pmhal_prcm_includes.h
 
file  pmhal_prcm_modinc.h
 
file  pmhal_prcm_stats.h
 This file contains the prototypes of the APIs present in the device abstraction layer file of PRCM status.
 
file  pmhal_prm_int.h
 This file contains the PRM Interrupt interface declarations. This file contains declarations of APIs which provide:
 
file  pmhal_rm.h
 This file contains the PRCM Reset Manager Interface APIs.
 
file  pmhal_sd.h
 This file contains the prototypes of the APIs present in the device abstraction layer file of Static Dependency Mangager.
 
file  pmhal_videopll.h
 This file contains enumeration declarations for different elements of videopll. This is only for tda2xx.
 
file  pmhal_vm.h
 This file contains the Voltage Manager API. This API supports OPP Voltage changes for all the voltage domains.
